text: Ureueng nyang hana geupeugot dacha Dacha nyang raya ngon keuji leupah Meulengkan nyang na dacha nyang cut-cut â€˜Oh Iheuh geupubuet meunyesai teulah Teuma Po gata ampon luah that Buet gata meuhat Neuteupue sudah Watee Neupeujeut gata di bumoe Neuteupue dum nyoe pakriban ulah Phon lam pruet ibu teuh ka Neuteupue Hana meusapeue pih na meuilah Teuma bek gata takheun droeteuh gleh Neuturi nyang gleh bandum le Allah Ureueng nyang takwa sit that Neuteusoe
